Neha
Welcome Neha!
Now give me a number:
165
Now give me another number:
164
The sum of 165 and 164 is 329.
The result of subtracting 164 from 165 is 1.
The product of 165 and 164 is 27060.
The result of dividing 165 by 164 is 1.00609756097561.
The remainder after dividing 165 by 164 is 1.
  
